        "description": {
          "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--3\"><p>A humanoid that comes within 5 feet of the weeping zombie must succeed on a [[/save ability=constitution dc=15]] saving throw or contract @disease[the Weeping Pox|GHMG|Weeping Pox]. If a humanoid succeeds on the saving throw, it's immune to the disease for 24 hours. A humanoid infected with the disease must repeat the saving throw every 24 hours, increasing its &amp;Reference[condition=exhaustion] level by one on a failure. This &amp;Reference[condition=exhaustion] can't be reduced until the disease is cured with magic.</p><div class=\"rd__spc-inline-post\"></div><p>Until the first level of &amp;Reference[condition=exhaustion] sets in, however, the humanoid has sharpened senses. Whenever this humanoid makes an ability check or saving throw against anything other than the disease, they can roll a [[/r d4]] and add the number rolled. A slight fever and overexcitement are the only signs this condition comes from @disease[the Weeping Pox|GHMG|Weeping Pox].</p></div>",
